  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will examine the effectiveness of group metacognitive therapy in comparison with
      group meditation therapy, in patients with Generalised Anxiety Disorder. Individuals will be
      randomly assigned to either meditation or metacognitive therapy and undergo 8 group therapy
      sessions of their respective treatment condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
